---
title: Teriyaki Chicken Drumsticks with Garlic Rice & Asian Veggies
description: Roasted in the oven and with tasty, slightly charred edges, chicken drumsticks are an easy and delicious way to enjoy
Asian-inspired flavours. Served with fragrant garlic rice plus crunchy greens and peanuts, this mild meal is a family winner!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/teriyaki-chicken-drumsticks-58080c9a.jpg
